Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.63,0:00:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,戌时已到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.50,0:00:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,犬夜叉马上要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.07,0:00:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,为了找齐四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.75,0:00:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,为了用这把铁碎牙打败奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.10,0:00:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,费尽千辛万苦\N总算到达白灵山圣地的深处的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.54,0:00:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,弥勒法师和珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.50,0:00:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到在那里\N存在着一股强烈的妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.57,0:00:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,快去救人  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.01,0:00:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,弥勒法师  珊瑚 七宝跟云母
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,穿梭于时空\N发生在战国时代与现代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.07,0:00:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:25.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:32.15,OP,,0,0,0,,分散在蓝蓝天空上的 七颗星星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:36.86,OP,,0,0,0,,每一颗星星 都刻着我的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.17,0:00:40.77,OP,,0,0,0,,就算梦想被粉碎 我也要寻找爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.07,0:00:44.80,OP,,0,0,0,,我无处可逃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:48.87,OP,,0,0,0,,紧紧抓着我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:57.30,OP,,0,0,0,,那些骗人的光阴 我再也不会输给它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:02.67,OP,,0,0,0,,睁大眼睛 看清楚这瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.67,0:01:06.85,OP,,0,0,0,,它仍然紧紧围绕着我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:10.85,OP,,0,0,0,,让人啜泣的 现实生活中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.85,0:01:14.85,OP,,0,0,0,,最重要的…到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:18.72,OP,,0,0,0,,繁忙的这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:22.95,OP,,0,0,0,,永恒的碎片 忽隐又忽现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:26.87,OP,,0,0,0,,去触摸 去捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:33.80,OP,,0,0,0,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:39.03,OP,,0,0,0,,为了得到最后的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:46.27,OP,,0,0,0,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:01.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在  瘦皮狼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.89,0:02:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没完呢  臭笨狗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.76,0:02:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢天谢地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.77,0:02:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.17,0:02:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要紧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以一直通到里面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.11,0:02:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.48,0:02:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有错的\N奈落一定就躲在这里面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道奈落\N就躲在神圣的结界里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的人都赶到了白灵山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.79,0:02:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要有重大的事发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第118话 白灵山里面又里面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.60,0:02:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股妖气越来越浓了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:03:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来白灵山神圣的结界\N里面的确藏着一股妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个回廊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奈落的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:27.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子\N它们好像也不打算躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奈落的毒虫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师  千万别发动风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你吸它们反而会中毒的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受制裁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为是我看错了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:52.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然真的是\N两个血肉之躯的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大胆的闯进这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来还以为
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会是\N犬夜叉这小子闯进来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个\N也算得上胆大包天了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.51,0:04:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别以为可以活着离开这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是要我们\N别再继续往前走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.39,0:04:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也就是表示\N奈落一定就在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  往这走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:31.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师  你还是先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么能这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.48,0:04:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首要之务\N是查出奈落的所在位置对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想袭击我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你见识我神乐用风的本事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个时候还东张西望啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要撑下去啊  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在那哭啊  法师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个人先逃\N说不定可以多活一阵子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法发动风穴对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在害怕\N那些会致命的虫毒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也未免太小看我弥勒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了自己心爱的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算要我赴汤蹈火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.01,0:06:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拼了这条命不要也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  真的发动风穴了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虫毒…发作了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢哦  弥勒法师跟珊瑚…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:06:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.91,0:07:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说  出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  你在这边等我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去走走观察一下情况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.42,0:07:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你胡说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉你不是\N无法进入圣地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:16.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.13,0:07:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为我真会\N被这个圣地给消灭掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你不要乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都不知道\N进了圣地会发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说那么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你乖乖在这等着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间讨论这些有的没的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  瘦皮狼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿帮了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.75,0:07:37.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭笨狗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.75,0:07:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我在这好好保护着戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底出了什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师跟珊瑚\N他们两个人上了白灵山
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在都还没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只好我自己去看一看了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟跟真的妖怪比起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣地应该\N比较不容易影响到我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.34,0:07:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无所谓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:07:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要走就快走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准搭她的肩\N也不准跟她说话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.41,0:08:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之\N要是戈薇出了什么事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:14.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会有危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算半妖也很难闯入圣地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你  千万不要逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比想象中还要困难
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要命的尽管上来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管来祭这个风穴好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:09:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来世间万物\N全都非常爱惜生命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个可恶的法师\N真的一点事都没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照理说应该透过风穴\N吸进了大量最猛胜的剧毒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法师那小子\N简直是自寻死路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一因此送了这条小命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.43,0:09:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没有办法再深入追究了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.23,0:09:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾  法师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落根本就不在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  不要再过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果再发动一次风穴的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:33.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里可以弄到衣服穿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别挡路  马上给我滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老娘就是不让
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件应该可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛇骨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听那班毒虫说\N睡骨已经死了是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡骨兄弟死得好惨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  蛮骨大师兄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个\N是睡骨留下来的纪念品
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛇骨  你真的肯给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大师兄你不是交代过\N一找到就要交出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛇骨  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是我的好兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世上\N值得我信任的只有你一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你这个人有点怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的结界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别以为这样就可以消灭我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是一点事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.39,0:12:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道真的没办法\N继续往前走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就走不动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:12:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你也是外强中干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.24,0:13:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼骨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都不像平常的你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然没发觉\N一直有人跟着你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是你这个家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你们七人帮\N人手不太够是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你光剩下一张嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.83,0:13:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定急着往前走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过继续往前走的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕连你这个半妖\N也会被消灭掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.77,0:13:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开炮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算收拾掉你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别得意得太早
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…还没…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖力消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天明明不是朔日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是结界的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这倒是出乎我意料之外
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本以为你会被结界消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.51,0:14:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然只是妖力消失而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.37,0:14:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好处不少嘛  身为一个半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然觉得身体轻松多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  光知道耍嘴皮子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是个人类小鬼罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小子  看你往哪跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能留在这里跟炼骨周旋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要想办法\N趁现在闯入山里面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.06,0:15:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我挨了一记飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法师他…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他发动了风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果吸了奈落毒虫的剧毒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.09,0:16:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒醒  求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我害他的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师  弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.97,0:16:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你  醒一醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  你醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  你先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.36,0:16:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只有你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不走\N我要留下来跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我这次\N是凶多吉少了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  就算只有你\N也一定要好好的活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.28,0:16:56.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我丢下你逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.38,0:16:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我宁愿跟你一起死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.33,0:17:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道为什么\N身体渐渐觉得轻松多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些妖怪\N为什么不过来攻击我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们似乎没办法靠近我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  这里是圣地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.86,0:17:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以\N连我体内的剧毒也被除掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.83,0:17:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看前面有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师  你可以走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子\N是不用一起死在这了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚刚…说了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.05,0:18:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你全都不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你能够跑多远
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.81,0:18:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开炮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.09,0:18:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无路可走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来  你的死期到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尸体不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃进岩石缝里面去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼骨师兄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.60,0:19:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是蛇骨你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会跑到这里来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七人帮\N就剩下我们几个了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到这件事还真伤脑筋耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.35,0:19:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下我们三个\N凑不足七个人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:20:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说要不要再取个新名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有…有件事问你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡骨身上的\N四魂之玉碎片怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.90,0:20:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.11,0:20:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经把它\N交给蛮骨大师兄啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子还真是没有私心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这样一来可就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.12,0:20:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的四魂之玉碎片\N全都到了蛮骨的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定连蛇骨的碎片迟早也…\N叫三人帮好像不够响亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不会让他得逞\N要叫三杰还是黑暗三人组哩…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.49,0:20:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛇骨  其实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情还真是越来越有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越来越有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.18,0:20:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山洞怎么这么深啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:20:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道一直通到最里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.09,0:21:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼骨师兄说的一点都没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.03,0:21:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的是犬夜叉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.23,0:21:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变回人类还是这么可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.57,0:21:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛇骨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.11,0:21:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.24,0:21:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等很久了\N和你一决胜负的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.10,0:21:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.65,0:23:37.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.35,0:22:13.33,ED,,0,0,0,,偷偷亲你一下 装作若无其事的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:18.40,ED,,0,0,0,,我这样调皮 是不是像个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.68,0:22:24.83,ED,,0,0,0,,早已习惯 被你说是娇嗔无理
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.83,0:22:34.55,ED,,0,0,0,,不过「喜欢你」这三个字却始终说不出口 My Sweet Emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.53,0:22:45.48,ED,,0,0,0,,对着镜子 多看一次 看看自己的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.25,0:22:58.78,ED,,0,0,0,,如果想飞奔出去追求刺激就得挺起胸膛向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.15,0:23:09.68,ED,,0,0,0,,大胆放手去做 直到满意为止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.85,0:23:18.73,ED,,0,0,0,,偷偷亲你一下 装作若无其事的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.73,0:23:23.90,ED,,0,0,0,,我这样调皮 是不是像个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.20,0:23:30.48,ED,,0,0,0,,早已习惯 被你说是娇嗔无理
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.48,0:23:39.95,ED,,0,0,0,,不过「喜欢你」这三个字却始终说不出口 My Sweet Emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.65,0:23:41.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
